	<script type="application/ld+json" class="yoast-schema-graph">{"@context":"https:\/\/schema.org","@graph":[{"@type":"Article","@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#article","isPartOf":{"@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/"},"author":{"name":"Kathryne Taylor","@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/#\/schema\/person\/c609c24a34a1976d0a3c1a1b0cd7f46a"},"headline":"Peach Cobbler with Almond Topping","datePublished":"2025-08-05T20:38:57+00:00","dateModified":"2025-08-21T02:12:52+00:00","wordCount":776,"commentCount":34,"publisher":{"@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/#organization"},"image":{"@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#primaryimage"},"thumbnailUrl":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/images\/2025\/08\/peach-cobbler-with-ice-cream.jpg","keywords":["almond flour","honey","peaches"],"articleSection":["dessert","gluten free","Independence Day","recipes","soy free","summer","tomato free"],"inLanguage":"en-US","potentialAction":[{"@type":"CommentAction","name":"Comment","target":["https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#respond"]}]},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/","url":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/","name":"Peach Cobbler with Almond Topping - Cookie and Kate","isPartOf":{"@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/#website"},"primaryImageOfPage":{"@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#primaryimage"},"image":{"@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#primaryimage"},"thumbnailUrl":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/images\/2025\/08\/peach-cobbler-with-ice-cream.jpg","datePublished":"2025-08-05T20:38:57+00:00","dateModified":"2025-08-21T02:12:52+00:00","description":"This peach cobbler recipe features bubbly ripe peaches underneath a tender, golden topping. It's made with almond flour, so it's gluten free.","breadcrumb":{"@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#breadcrumb"},"inLanguage":"en-US","potentialAction":[{"@type":"ReadAction","target":["https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/"]}]},{"@type":"ImageObject","inLanguage":"en-US","@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#primaryimage","url":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/images\/2025\/08\/peach-cobbler-with-ice-cream.jpg","contentUrl":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/images\/2025\/08\/peach-cobbler-with-ice-cream.jpg","width":1200,"height":1800,"caption":"peach cobbler with ice cream"},{"@type":"BreadcrumbList","@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#breadcrumb","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"name":"recipes","item":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/category\/food-recipes\/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"name":"dessert","item":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/category\/food-recipes\/dessert\/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":3,"name":"Peach Cobbler with Almond Topping"}]},{"@type":"WebSite","@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/#website","url":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/","name":"Cookie and Kate","description":"Whole Foods and Vegetarian Recipe Blog","publisher":{"@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/#organization"},"potentialAction":[{"@type":"SearchAction","target":{"@type":"EntryPoint","urlTemplate":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/?s={search_term_string}"},"query-input":{"@type":"PropertyValueSpecification","valueRequired":true,"valueName":"search_term_string"}}],"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Organization","@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/#organization","name":"Cookie and Kate","url":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","inLanguage":"en-US","@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/#\/schema\/logo\/image\/","url":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/images\/2024\/10\/logo-696.png","contentUrl":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/images\/2024\/10\/logo-696.png","width":696,"height":696,"caption":"Cookie and Kate"},"image":{"@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/#\/schema\/logo\/image\/"},"sameAs":["https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/cookieandkate","https:\/\/x.com\/cookieandkate","https:\/\/instagram.com\/cookieandkate","https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/in\/kathryne-taylor-20012213\/","https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/cookieandkate\/","https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/user\/cookieandkate\/"]},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/#\/schema\/person\/c609c24a34a1976d0a3c1a1b0cd7f46a","name":"Kathryne Taylor","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","inLanguage":"en-US","@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/images\/2024\/10\/cropped-kathryne-taylor-200-96x96.jpg","url":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/images\/2024\/10\/cropped-kathryne-taylor-200-96x96.jpg","contentUrl":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/images\/2024\/10\/cropped-kathryne-taylor-200-96x96.jpg","caption":"Kathryne Taylor"},"description":"I'm a vegetable enthusiast, dog lover, mother and bestselling cookbook author. I've been sharing recipes here on Cookie and Kate since 2010, and I'm always cooking something new in my Kansas City kitchen. Cook with me!","sameAs":["https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/about\/"]},{"@context":"https:\/\/schema.org\/","@type":"Recipe","name":"Peach Cobbler with Almond Topping","description":"This peach cobbler recipe features bubbly ripe peaches underneath a perfectly golden topping. The topping is made of almond flour, which offers lovely flavor and makes the recipe gluten free. Recipe yields about 9 modest servings.","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Cookie and Kate","url":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/about\/"},"keywords":"peach cobbler, almond flour cobbler","image":["https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/images\/2025\/08\/peach-cobbler-with-ice-cream-225x225.jpg","https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/images\/2025\/08\/peach-cobbler-with-ice-cream-260x195.jpg","https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/images\/2025\/08\/peach-cobbler-with-ice-cream-320x180.jpg","https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/images\/2025\/08\/peach-cobbler-with-ice-cream.jpg"],"url":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/","recipeIngredient":["2 &frac12; pounds ripe peaches, peeled* and cut into 1-inch chunks (about 6 medium-to-large)","3 tablespoons honey","2 tablespoons arrowroot starch or cornstarch","1 teaspoon vanilla extract","½ teaspoon ground cinnamon","2 ½ cups (225 grams) blanched almond flour** ","1 tablespoon baking powder","¼ teaspoon fine salt","3 tablespoons granulated sugar","Zest from 1 large lemon ","5 tablespoons cold unsalted butter","2 tablespoons plain whole-milk Greek yogurt","1 large egg","Optional: 1 teaspoon turbinado sugar (raw sugar) for sprinkling on top","Vanilla ice cream or whipped cream, for serving"],"recipeInstructions":[{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit, then make the filling: In a 9-inch square baking dish, mix together the peaches, honey, starch, vanilla and cinnamon. Bake the filling for 20 to 25 minutes, until the mixture is bubbling around all four edges. ","url":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#instruction-step-1"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Meanwhile, prepare the topping: in a mixing bowl, combine the almond flour, baking powder and salt. Whisk gently until combined, and set it aside. ","url":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#instruction-step-2"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"In a small-to-medium bowl, combine the sugar and lemon zest. Use your fingers to rub the zest into the sugar (this extracts more flavor from the lemon). Then, pour the mixture into the other dry ingredients and whisk to combine. Keep the bowl handy for the egg mixture. ","url":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#instruction-step-3"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Grate the butter on the large holes of a cheese grater into the flour, stirring as you grate so the butter doesn’t clump.","url":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#instruction-step-4"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"In the smaller bowl, combine the yogurt and egg, and whisk until evenly combined. Pour the wet mixture into the dry mixture, and stir until well combined. It will look crumbly at first, but stir well until it comes together into a cohesive dough with streaks of butter. ","url":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#instruction-step-5"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Dollop one spoonful at a time over the hot filling, using the back of another spoon or your finger to help transfer each dollop. Sprinkle the turbinado sugar evenly over the dough, if using. ","url":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#instruction-step-6"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Bake 17 to 20 minutes until the filling is actively bubbling around the edges and the top is lightly golden. Let the cobbler rest for 5 to 10 minutes before serving. Serve with vanilla ice cream or whipped cream, if desired.","url":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#instruction-step-7"}],"prepTime":"PT20M","cookTime":"PT40M","totalTime":"PT1H","recipeYield":["9","9 servings"],"recipeCategory":"Dessert","cookingMethod":"Baked","recipeCuisine":"American","suitableForDiet":"GlutenFreeDiet","aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","reviewCount":"9","ratingValue":"4.7"},"nutrition":{"servingSize":"1 serving (no ice cream)","calories":"334 calories","sugarContent":"22.4 g","sodiumContent":"76.6 mg","fatContent":"19.7 g","saturatedFatContent":"5.4 g","transFatContent":"0 g","carbohydrateContent":"31.9 g","fiberContent":"5.4 g","proteinContent":"9 g","cholesterolContent":"38.1 mg","@type":"nutritionInformation"},"video":{"@context":"http:\/\/schema.org","@type":"VideoObject","name":"”Peach","description":"”Watch","contentUrl":"https:\/\/content.jwplatform.com\/videos\/&rdquo;qhXiYlJc&rdquo;.mp4","thumbnailUrl":["https:\/\/content.jwplatform.com\/thumbs\/&rdquo;qhXiYlJc&rdquo;-720.jpg"],"uploadDate":"1970-01-01T00:00:00+00:00"},"review":[{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Regan Brown"},"datePublished":"2025-08-05","reviewBody":"I can’t wait to try this!"},{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Mooinca"},"datePublished":"2025-08-05","reviewBody":"What could I replace the egg with? Looks so yummy. I LOVE Almond Flour!"},{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"SJB"},"datePublished":"2025-08-07","reviewBody":"It was every bit as delicious as I hoped it would be!"},{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"3"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Paula"},"datePublished":"2025-08-09","reviewBody":"My peach cobbler did not turn out so well. I have so much left over topping - at least half of the bowl. The little dollops look like madelines on top of the peaches. No idea what I didn't do correctly. My dry mixture never formed a cohesive dough once the wet ingredients were added. Shaving the butter with a box cutter seems unnecessary. I did it for 4 tbls but used butter at table top temperature for the last tbls. It mixed in fine. I like your recipes and have tried many with success -- just not this one."},{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Denise"},"datePublished":"2025-08-10","reviewBody":"Utterly delicious, thanks for another great recipe!"},{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Dianne Lemieux"},"datePublished":"2025-08-11","reviewBody":"This was my very first cobbler and it got rave reviews! Loved that it is gluten free so that it was safe for my daughter to enjoy as well. The almond topping was soooo good. This recipe is going into my \"keeper\" folder. Thanks once again Kate. Actually, I never made one of your recipes that wasn't a keeper! Look forward to the next one."},{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Laurie McLane-Higginson"},"datePublished":"2025-08-14","reviewBody":"Kate,\r\nI made this peach cobbler for friends and they all loved it! The almond flour makes such a wonderful flavorful topping. I also added some blueberries to add more flavor and color. Thank you!"},{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"VD"},"datePublished":"2025-08-26","reviewBody":"I made this as a dessert for special guests after lunch, and it was a huge hit! Everyone, including my family, absolutely loved it. I also really appreciate the gluten-free option, as I’m gluten-sensitive - it made enjoying this treat worry-free!"},{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"4"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Stacy"},"datePublished":"2025-08-30","reviewBody":"Very good though I would not make again.   Liked the filling more than the crust."}],"datePublished":"2025-08-05","@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#recipe","isPartOf":{"@id":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/#article"},"mainEntityOfPage":"https:\/\/cookieandkate.com\/peach-cobbler\/"}]}</script>
