	<h2 id="comments-list" class="comments-title">Comments</h2><ol class="comment-list">	<li id="comment-904522" class="comment even thread-even depth-1 parent">
		<article id="div-comment-904522" class="comment-body">
			<footer class="comment-meta">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
										<b class="fn">Brenda</b>				</div><!-- .comment-author -->

				<div class="comment-metadata">
					<time datetime="2025-08-05T16:26:34-05:00">August 5, 2025 at 4:26 PM</time>				</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

							</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>Allergy to nuts so cannot use the almond flour&#8230; any other suggestions?</p>
			</div><!-- .comment-content -->

			<div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-904522" data-commentid="904522" data-postid="46896" data-belowelement="div-comment-904522" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Brenda" aria-label="Reply to Brenda">Reply</a></div>		</article><!-- .comment-body -->
	<ol class="children">
	<li id="comment-904543" class="comment byuser comment-author-megan odd alt depth-2 staff">
		<article id="div-comment-904543" class="comment-body">
			<footer class="comment-meta">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
										<b class="fn">Cookie and Kate</b>				</div><!-- .comment-author -->

				<div class="comment-metadata">
					<time datetime="2025-08-05T17:58:27-05:00">August 5, 2025 at 5:58 PM</time>				</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

							</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>Hi Brenda, you could use another type of flour, but almond flour is denser so it wouldn&#8217;t be a 1:1. You would have better luck starting with a recipe designed to be used with a flour type that works for you.</p>
			</div><!-- .comment-content -->

			<div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-904543" data-commentid="904543" data-postid="46896" data-belowelement="div-comment-904543" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Cookie and Kate" aria-label="Reply to Cookie and Kate">Reply</a></div>		</article><!-- .comment-body -->
	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
</ol><!-- .children -->
</li><!-- #comment-## -->
